Insurance
To benefit from new and enhanced Insurance Policy features, harmonize existing data and move to the Salesforce data model.

You can switch to the FSC Insurance Policy object model from the Asset-based or Insurance Industries Extension object models. Services and LWCs are updated to work with insurance policy data in the Salesforce data model.

Insurance Policy Harmonization Overview
Insurance Industries Extension to Insurance Policy Object Model Mapping
Asset to Insurance Policy Object Model Mapping

Learn how fields correspond when moving data between models. Use these field mappings when creating scripts that move insurance policy data from one model to the other.
